{
  "stem": "9262.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And downstairs, I think you had-- one, two, three, four-- you had four.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in our little place, you had nine rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then out in the yard, on both sides, you had about six families on one side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you had the larger block, where they had also first floor, but it went round like a L-shape.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Altogether, they had about 38 apartments-- what they call apartments-- rooms, 38 rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what about toilet and washing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Toilet was in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The water was obtainable from the well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the-- and the rooms had nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just bare rooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cooking-- we had to get a little stove, one very ancient stove that could go in a museum and would fetch by today's standard an enormous sum in the antique market.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, it was a real old piece of history, that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were cooking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, in order to get it installed-- as I said before, you see, the Poles were not doing any jobs for Jews-- there was someone living on-- in-- well, he was living in our courtyard.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He actually came from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was, I think, an engineer before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was able to erect a stove for us with a flue, like a pipe, a flue going outside, so that if we had any wood, or any coal, or whatever things, we could put it in, and it would give heat.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could cook on it and at the same time obtain heat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came in the ghetto-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's before we came into the ghetto, we were still living in town, my father went to these secondhand shops, which the Poles already owned.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the war, it was owned by Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
